---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Dashboard Cleaning Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional dashboard cleaning in Fort Lauderdale. Mobile service - we come to you! Removes dust and protects against UV damage. Same-day appointments. Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}upholstery-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Upholstery Cleaning Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Dashboard Cleaning Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional dashboard cleaning removes dust, grime, and fingerprints while adding UV protection against Florida's intense sun."
  currentPage="/dashboard-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Your dashboard takes the worst sun exposure of any interior surface. In Fort Lauderdale, that means year-round UV bombardment that fades color, dries out vinyl, and eventually causes cracking. A dusty dashboard also looks neglected and can trigger allergies when your AC blows particles around the cabin.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We bring our dashboard cleaning service directly to your home or office anywhere in Fort Lauderdale. Whether you live near the Boatyard neighborhood or out by Plantation, we come to you with professional products that clean and protect in one visit.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Dashboard cleaning includes your entire front dash areaâ€”the main surface, instrument cluster, center console, vents, screens, and all the trim pieces that collect dust and fingerprints.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does Dashboard Cleaning Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Dashboard cleaning in Fort Lauderdale costs $30 to $50 depending on your vehicle's interior complexity.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Basic interiors with simple dash layouts fall on the lower end. Luxury vehicles with multiple screens, intricate trim pieces, and textured surfaces take more time and care, which affects pricing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Most clients add dashboard cleaning to other interior services like vacuuming or leather care. We can bundle services for better value.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does Dashboard Cleaning Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Dashboard cleaning takes about 30 minutes for most vehicles, with protection lasting 4-6 weeks.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We work through each section of your dashboard methodically. Vents need special attention because dust collects deep inside. Screens require gentle cleaning with products that won't leave residue or damage displays. Textured surfaces trap dust and need proper agitation to release it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Your car is ready to drive immediately after we finish.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Why Does Your Dashboard Need Professional Cleaning?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Florida sun damages unprotected dashboards faster than anywhere else. UV rays fade color, dry out materials, and cause cracking that ruins your interior.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Dashboards are made from vinyl, plastic, and rubber compounds that break down under UV exposure. Without protection, these materials:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Fade from black or gray to a chalky lighter color</li>
          <li>Become brittle and develop cracks</li>
          <li>Shrink slightly, causing gaps and squeaks</li>
          <li>Release chemicals that create that film on your windshield</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Beyond sun damage, a dirty dashboard affects your driving experience. Dust particles blow through your vents and into your lungs. Grime on screens makes them harder to read. Sticky residue on controls feels unpleasant every time you adjust something.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Signs your dashboard needs attention:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
          <li>Visible dust layer on surfaces</li>
          <li>Faded or grayish color on trim pieces</li>
          <li>Fingerprints and smudges on screens</li>
          <li>Sticky feeling on buttons and controls</li>
          <li>Film buildup on inside of windshield</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Our Dashboard Cleaning Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Dust Removal</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We start with soft brushes to dislodge dust from vents, crevices, and textured surfaces without scratching.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Surface Cleaning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We apply Chemical Guys Total Interior cleaner to dissolve grime, oils, and sticky residue from all dashboard surfaces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Detail Work</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Cotton swabs and detailing brushes reach into buttons, vents, and tight areas around screens and controls.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">Screen Care</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Touchscreens and instrument clusters get gentle cleaning with products that won't leave streaks or damage displays.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1e3a5f]">UV Protection</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We apply Chemical Guys Silk Shine protectant for a natural satin finish. This non-greasy formula blocks UV rays without that shiny, artificial look.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-2">Faded Dashboard?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          For severely faded dashboards, we can apply VRP (Vinyl, Rubber, Plastic) restorer to bring back the original dark color before protecting.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Dashboard Cleaning Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c9a227] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$30-$50 depending on complexity</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">About 30 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">UV protection included</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Screen-safe products</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Protection lasts 4-6 weeks</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Dashboard Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}interior-vacuuming-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Interior Vacuuming</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}interior-protection-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Interior Protection</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}leather-conditioning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Leather Conditioning</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}full-detail-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Full Detail</a></li>
